title: Banjar Al-Dosari
text:
Banjar Mohammed Al Dosari (born 8 August 1981) is a <a href="Qatar">Qatar</a>i <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Referee%20%28association%20football%29">referee</a> who has been a full international referee for <a href="FIFA">FIFA</a>.
Al Dosari was a FIFA referee from 2008 to 2016. He has served as a referee at competitions including the <a href="2014%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20qualification%20%28AFC%29">2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers</a>, beginning with the preliminary-round match between <a href="Palestine%20national%20football%20team">Palestine</a> and <a href="Afghanistan%20national%20football%20team">Afghanistan</a>.
